{"tid":2411421,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"明日開始放寬晚市堂食？10宗源頭不明本地個案　部分患者從事飲食業","createTime":"2021-02-17T10:15:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T10:15:04.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3987a9154042cff524814def5e976c6ca6093acd","tid":2411421,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T10:15:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576069-20210217.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576069-20210217.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=bV20Ktv%2Bt3m81RcJrVEN28jT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=995a6d81\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1576069-20210217.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d52e0e06\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1576069-20210217.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n本港新增16宗確診個案，有10宗屬源頭不明本地個案，當中部分患者從事飲食業，亦有長者護養院的員工屬初步確診。<br />\n<br />\n其中在荃灣海壩街都好燒臘茶餐廳，有做燒臘的廚師確診，11名同事要檢疫。另外，廣華街廣發商業中心一個廚房亦有員工確診，9名緊密接觸者要檢疫。天后的御名軒有知客初步確診，暫時未知源頭。<br />\n<br />\n初步陽性個案中，包括圓玄護養院暨長者日間護理中心一名護理員，患者主要在3樓工作，有50名院友及約30名員工需要做檢疫。"}]}